divs: sighting detailshi, this isn't actually my sighting. this was relayed to me by my sister. she was coming home from her job yesterday between 6 and 6:30 a.m. (she works the graveyard shift.) as she was listening to the radio (103.3 fm) a number of people were calling in saying they saw a triangular shaped series of lights hovering overhead. they had been hovering for quite some time. my sister said she saw it to the west. one of the callers on the radio claimed he saw\heard air national guard jets going to intercept the object. how much of this is true is unknown to me at this point. i have yet to have a chance to call the p.a.n.g. air base and p.d.x. to confirm any of this. i also haven't seen or read anything about this in the local media. i write a blog, ufo-skeptical believer, and would like to know if you have any information about this incident. you can call me at the number i listed or email me. hans
